<p><font face="Verdana" size="5">Call Context: Similar to contexts being 
represented as objects</font></p>

<p><font face="Verdana" size="5"> 
Causalities are represented as Call Context objects</font></p>

<p><font face="Verdana" size="5">
</font></p>

<p><font face="Verdana" size="5" color="#FF0000">Key point:</font></p>

<p><font face="Verdana" size="5" color="#FF0000">Object Contexts are used to 
model the space an object lives in and
Call Contexts are used to model 
the work being done in that space
in a transparent manner</font></p>

